parameters: Rei: Ah... I'm already out of magical power...
Rei: Pull yourself together, Rei Granford. There's still more...

Rei: Why... despite all this practice with magic, I'm not improving at
all.
Rei: It's too late for such magic... Anyone can do it.

Magic School Student 1: Teehee... Miss Granford, you're still trying
so hard.

Magic School Student 2: I mean, I could use Fire from the beginning.
Ahaha!

Magic School Student 3: Don't say it like that. Rei is working really
hard. It's sad to have no talent. Teehee...

Magic School Student 1: Miss Granford, you should become an idol
instead of a sorceress. You've received another idol offer recently,
haven't you?

Rei: I'm not interested in being an idol. I will definitely graduate
from the magic school.
Magic School Student 3: But sorcery doesn't suit you. Teehee...

Magic School Student 2: I think being an idol suits you better?
Teehee...

Runo: You guys! Stop picking on Rei and bullying her! Go away! Get out
of here!
